# LifeSmart OmniPlatform - Project Overview

**Project**: LifeSmart educational platform (finance, life balance, quizzes, budget tools)
**Stack**: React 18, Create React App (CRA + Craco), Firebase (Auth, Firestore, Analytics)

## Tech Stack
- **UI**: React 18, React Router v6, Radix UI primitives, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion
- **Backend**: Firebase Auth, Firestore, Firebase Analytics
- **Build**: Craco (webpack alias), Babel, PostCSS
- **Path alias**: `@/*` → `./src/*` (use `@/components/...`, `@/lib/...`)

## Key Conventions
- JavaScript (no TypeScript)
- Functional components and hooks only
- Single-page app with client-side routing
